high_descs: Walk straight and turn around 180 degrees to the left until you are facing the sink.
Put the fork in front of you.
Turn 90 degrees to the bowl.
Walk forward and put the fork in the bowl.
Take the bowl off of the shelf in front of you.
Turn around and stand at the edge of the sink holding the bowl in front of the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Walk to the shelf, grab a fork and put it in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Walk straight and head to the larger sink at the end of the counter.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn right to reach the bowl.
Place the fork in the bowl on the top shelf of the fridge.
Take out the bowl from the fridge.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the Fork in the Bowl and place it in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Take the fork out of the sink.
Go to the refrigerator.
Put the fork in the bowl in the refrigerator.
Take the bowl out of the refrigerator.
Go to the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a Fork and a Bowl in the SinkBasin.
